TERMS OF USE:

PERMITTED USES:
✅ Educational demonstrations of Cloudflare security features
✅ Security training and awareness programs  
✅ Controlled testing environments and laboratories
✅ Academic research and coursework
✅ Security conference presentations and workshops
✅ Internal corporate training sessions

PROHIBITED USES:
❌ Production deployment of any kind
❌ Processing real customer or personal data
❌ Commercial use without proper security measures
❌ Public deployment without Cloudflare protection
❌ Use in environments containing sensitive information
❌ Integration with real payment or financial systems
❌ Any use that could expose real users to security risks

